# {{ project_name }}

A Databricks Mosaic AI agent project scaffolded by [dex](https://github.com/yarrib/dex).

## Setup

```bash
uv sync
```

## Project Structure

```
{{ project_name }}/
├── src/{{ project_name }}/
│   ├── agent.py               # Agent definition (LangChain / MLflow)
│   └── tools/
│       ├── __init__.py        # Tool registry
{% if include_vector_search %}│       └── retriever.py       # Vector search retriever tool
{% endif %}{% if include_notebook %}├── notebooks/
│   └── evaluate_agent.py      # Interactive evaluation notebook
{% endif %}├── resources/                 # Serving endpoint definition
├── tests/                     # Tests
├── databricks.yml             # Databricks Asset Bundle config
└── pyproject.toml             # Project config
```

## Development

```bash
# Run tests
uv run pytest

# Lint
uv run ruff check .

# Format
uv run ruff format .
```

## Deploy

```bash
# Deploy to dev (default target)
databricks bundle deploy

# Deploy model serving endpoint
databricks bundle run {{ project_name }}_serving_endpoint

# Deploy to prod
databricks bundle deploy --target prod
```
